            "subtitle": "AUSTRALIAN SWIMWEAR BRAND",
            "title": "Thank you FAE 🖤",
            "content": "<p>We would like to give a special shout-out to FAE for allowing us to use their incredible content for our Sahara theme. </p><p>Follow <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/fae/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.instagram.com/fae/\">@FAE</a> on Instagram and visit their website via this <a href=\"https://www.fae.house/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.fae.house/\">link</a>.</p><p>---</p><p>Sahara theme is made with 🖤 <br/>by Shopify agency <a href=\"https://digifist.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://digifist.com/\">DigiFist</a>.</p>",
            "button_style": "button--filled",
